  "detailed_description": "Escape a cyber-hell while <strong>chatting</strong> with a neural net <strong>Artificial Intelligence</strong>.<br>Speak through the <strong>microphone</strong> or type on the <strong>keyboard</strong>. You choose.<br><br>Strange Aeons is a 1-1.5 hour experimental game available for <strong>both 2D screens and VR</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/f81751812dc5853d7d7d4fa713e9967a.poster.avif?t=1765385584\" width=480 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/f81751812dc5853d7d7d4fa713e9967a.webm?t=1765385584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>The followers of your cult are summoning you. You must escape this netherworld and reign in your rightful domain in the land of the living. Engage in a strange ritual by speaking with a mysterious Artificial Intelligence. Figure out why you were banished and cast out to hell in the first place.<br><br>There is no other way out.<br><br><i>Strange Aeons is a neural-net-AI, speech-to-text and text-to-speech powered experience. All of this works offline, without a back-end server or internet connectivity.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/728458f9fed68050a5eb4f45c14788ed.avif?t=1765385584\" width=480 height=160 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Microphone & Keyboard controls<br></li><li>Neural Net AI<br></li><li>Procedural music<br></li><li>Imaginary languages<br></li><li>Optional VR mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/da70834a8491fa91051b9d339e79038e.avif?t=1765385584\" width=480 height=160 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Speech recognition may be inaccurate for some voices - consider using keyboard input if you find your words not understood well enough<br></li><li>Make sure the microphone is not clipping</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/3b1933e3a57d4b1918df35a6b6b5dc53.poster.avif?t=1765385584\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/3b1933e3a57d4b1918df35a6b6b5dc53.webm?t=1765385584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/3b1933e3a57d4b1918df35a6b6b5dc53.mp4?t=1765385584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Escape a cyber-hell while <strong>chatting</strong> with a neural net <strong>Artificial Intelligence</strong>.<br>Speak through the <strong>microphone</strong> or type on the <strong>keyboard</strong>. You choose.<br><br>Strange Aeons is a 1-1.5 hour experimental game available for <strong>both 2D screens and VR</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/f81751812dc5853d7d7d4fa713e9967a.poster.avif?t=1765385584\" width=480 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/f81751812dc5853d7d7d4fa713e9967a.webm?t=1765385584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>The followers of your cult are summoning you. You must escape this netherworld and reign in your rightful domain in the land of the living. Engage in a strange ritual by speaking with a mysterious Artificial Intelligence. Figure out why you were banished and cast out to hell in the first place.<br><br>There is no other way out.<br><br><i>Strange Aeons is a neural-net-AI, speech-to-text and text-to-speech powered experience. All of this works offline, without a back-end server or internet connectivity.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/728458f9fed68050a5eb4f45c14788ed.avif?t=1765385584\" width=480 height=160 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Microphone & Keyboard controls<br></li><li>Neural Net AI<br></li><li>Procedural music<br></li><li>Imaginary languages<br></li><li>Optional VR mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/da70834a8491fa91051b9d339e79038e.avif?t=1765385584\" width=480 height=160 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Speech recognition may be inaccurate for some voices - consider using keyboard input if you find your words not understood well enough<br></li><li>Make sure the microphone is not clipping</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/3b1933e3a57d4b1918df35a6b6b5dc53.poster.avif?t=1765385584\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/3b1933e3a57d4b1918df35a6b6b5dc53.webm?t=1765385584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290960/extras/3b1933e3a57d4b1918df35a6b6b5dc53.mp4?t=1765385584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
